  m_text: "[TEST] \n[TAB to toggle instructions]\nHow to use: \nCLICK on grass with
    selection -> place down item\nPress R -> Control troop mode\nCLICK on a tile
    while controlling -> control troops\nRIGHT CLICK on object or tile -> item information\nX
    + HOVER on object -> delete\nWASD -> move camera\n\"T\" -> Zoom in camera\n\"Y\"
    -> Zoom out camera\n\"G\" -> Reset Camera\n\"Escape\" -> Option to go back to
    menu\n\nFeedback helps this project a lot :)\n"
